                  1
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800">Free Online Assessment</h2>
              </div>
              <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-slate-700 font-medium mb-4 md:mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                Start your journey from the comfort of your home. Our specialists review your photos, 
                medical history, and goals to create a personalized treatment plan.
              </p>
              
